org.apache.fineract.infrastructure.core.api

Class JsonCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.fineract.infrastructure.core.api.JsonCommand

  • public final class JsonCommand
extends java.lang.Object
    Immutable representation of a command. Wraps the provided JSON with convenience functions for extracting parameter values and checking for changes against an existing value.
